+------------------+
|  Manual cases:   |
+------------------+

1. Page is displayed as expected and headers (for locations, jobs etc) are displayed properly.
2. All location  links are functioning properly
3. For every location verify that the the drop-down filtered jobs by department / search string
4. For the main page verify that the drop-down filtered jobs by location / department / open -search
5. For every job, verify that that more text is displayed properly when key > pressed.
6. For every job, verify that when extra text is opened you can email / close it. 
7. Verify that the easy-helper on right button is opened as expected
8. Verify that you can upload files to the easy-helper on right button is opened as expected
9. Verify that the Resume-upload is functioning properly
10. Verify the Home button is working